\ip Ia nuk 48 Jemes r…®m…ôkupw…ôn m…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i ia n…ôkuku…ô me pam ia Niutestamen. Jemes in pi…ôvi Iesu. In i…ôm…ô asori riti ia n…ôm…ô asori me s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me fwe Jerusalem. N…ôkuku…ô s…ôv…ônhi rev…ôn t…® nakalasia me pam r…®pkev…ôn mh…ô t…® nous…ôs…®mw…®nien s…ôv…ônraha kuatia. Jemes r…®m…ôrai n…ôkuku…ô i m…ô trahat…ôn nakalasia me ia noien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamhahat…ôt…ô ia Kristo. In r…®ni m…ô tr…®ni m…®nu…ô nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ôi i…ôrmama riti ro n…®p…ôrhienien, tuk…ôtoni ia noien s…ôv…ônhi. Jemes ramahat…ôn n…ôrmama ia narimnari me m…®ni m…ô niemaha tr…ôpw…ôh n…ôpiien ir…ôha. Ir…ôha tuh…ôpw…ôh n…®ni …ôr…ôhaien ir…ôha me. Ir…ôha tuho r…ômn…ômwhen a ia nir…ôha me. Ir…ôha tuh…ôtui amasan t…® n…ôfe n…ôram…®nraha rani. Ir…ôha tuh…ôpw…ôh n…ôfi…ôut…ôien ir…ôha. Ir…ôha tuho n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha r…ôpw…ômw…®s n…ôn…ô mh…ôfwaki.
