\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Kal 1:19, Wok Me 15:23, 1Tes 1:1\x*Iou Jemes. Iou i…ôrmama riti s…ô iakamo tukwini nari m Kumwes…ôn m…®ne Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha. Iakam…ôrhi pehe n…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukumiaha kw…ôn…ôkwus twelef s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel hiamar…ô k…®rk…®ri ia t…ôn…ômt…ôn…ô me. Iakani ramasan tukumiaha.
