\v 19 Piak keikei me, rer…®miaha tramrhi n…ô…°kiariien i. N…ôp…®n k…®miaha hiam…ô…°kiari, tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôt…ôr…®…° amasan, mh…ôpw…ôh n…ô…°kiari akwauakwien. K…®miaha tih…ôpw…ôh n…ôseniien niemaha r…ôpi akwauakw k…®miaha,
