\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Kol 3:8, 1Tes 2:1\x*K…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôrarki raka noien me pam s…ôm…ôme h…ômkem…®k m…®ne noien …ôr…ôha me n…ôha h…ôp…®k ia n…®m…®ruien s…ôk…®miaha. Tiheiwaiu mh…ôt…ôr…®…° amasan t…® n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha k…®n…ôpwei r…ômwhen ia nuni nari ia rer…®miaha. N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha rukur…ôn nuvehim…®ruien k…®miaha.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Mat 7:26, Rom 2:13\x*M…ôt…ô tiham…ôkeikei mho n…ôfe n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha rani. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô k…®miaha hiam…ôt…ôr…®…° a ir…ô, hiameiku…ô atukw a ia k…®miaha.
