\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Rom 2:1, 14:4\x*I…ôrmama kuatia in …ôpa rauvehi nasoriien m…ô tr…ômri Loa, m…ôkiri noien me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama, n…ôn…ô m…ôrpw…®n tai noien me s…ôv…ônraha. I…ôrmama n…ôha in n…ôha rauvehim…®ru n…ôrmama, mamouraha mwi ir…ôha. M…ôt…ô ik sin i? R…ôfo ikam…ôkiri noien me s…ôv…ôi piam?
